# Git Conventions

## Commit messages

Use **Conventional Commits** format:

```
feat: add python-fastapi demo
fix: correct Dockerfile for rust-axum
docs: update root README with new demo list
test: add endpoint test for typescript-bun
chore: add .gitignore
```

## Granularity

Flexible — use your judgment. One commit per demo is fine, splitting structure/code/tests is also fine.
